Oh yes, quite a lot persuasion yes. I - I was a poor eater you see, and you see the food was good and they knew it was good but - I didn't like - the - the - that - part of it - I don't remember whatever else there was, b}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126017\charrsid16660515 ut I was supposed to be a bit c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 addy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 If for example you didn't eat your main course, would you still get some of the pudding to follow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh yes - oh I don't think we penalized to that extent, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 But it was definitely disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh disapproved of because I didn't take what was good for me. Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 What about holding your implements and how you sat, were they particular about that or didn't they mind how you sat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh well - there would have been a fair amount of discipline but - I don't think there was any undue - regulation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 But you were to sit straight at the table?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh yes, oh yes, we were supposed to behave - reasonably - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Could you bring a toy or book to the table during a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 I don't think - I don't think we would have wanted to actually, no.
