Ah, some people would have been, some people would have been, yes, very strict Free Church people, but - our people - were never strict like in that sense. They would go down themselves - father go down with us. And we had visitors - a beautiful pla
ce you see, you know what Ardroyle is like you know, we had this big stre}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16523904\charrsid16660515 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 
ch and - farm houses were perhaps a mile away from the shore. And - it was - very enjoyable thing, used to go down to the shore, and - play down there for a while. Beautiful flowers?
