I didn't - swimming wasn't very easy from our - there was only one little pool in the rocks, really, the - the shore was very dangerous and very rough. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 So did you not learn to swim?
