\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Well, I went to - school to the Nich - I came to the secondary at nine - at fourteen, or just before I was fourt
