d then - when - I remember first - it was a local man who was the schoolmaster, and he was a great friend of his and he had access of the - by the time - Coates of Paisley had gifted libraries to all the schools, and - I remember seeing a lot of - Alexand
er Dumas books, you know - The Three Musk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16523904\charrsid16660515 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 
