n but they brought up the - the - my aunt had lost her - her only child and she - couldn't have any more, and the - they brought up - the daughter of I think an uncle of mine who had died in Glasgow and - then - a niece of her husband's as well who - whos
e
 home was in the village, they - stayed in the house but they never - there was no any - never any formal adoption but they was brought up as two - daughters you see. Yes, and I used to go there. And he was the man who brought the first - Ford - Model T t
