ired everything there was to be - read on - on - Ford at that time and used to get - magazines like the Motor and - I - I used to revel in this. And - I knew the - innards of the Ford car from - from as far as you could - acquire that from books, quite ea
r
ly on. And I suppose when I was in school here I must have been one of the very very few pupils who had a licence, I got a licence when I was seventeen, but - I had been quite a - an accomplished driver by that time, driving with my friend back and forth 
