\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Yes, well of course - it was qui
te an accomplishment because not everybody had the opportunity and I wouldn't have had it only we happened to be friendly with this chap who - who happened to be an old - employee of - of my - father.
