n McLeod, my - yes his - his mother was brought up in a village - not very far from us in Borve}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16523904\charrsid16660515 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 
 and she was very friendly with her. I don't know was her bridesmaid at her wedding but she was - if she wasn't she was - very - much - very close to her, yes.
