s round about, you know, they came whenever - the spirit moved them and that was all right. Then of course at Communion times, this was a time - in - in - in my youth, when there was a great movement of population - they have here the communions you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Could you tell me about that?
