\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh - no, no, you could pick up - well as I say, the minister, the schoolmaster, policeman, and - they kind of stood apart and
 that - that was it - I don't know that's really as far as - that there was a class distinction just by virtue of their offices - they were - marked men you might say and that was it. That - I wouldn't say that they were - oh they were given - they were a
ll given a good deal of respect - because of their - offices.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 What about your father and his offices and his standing?
