Well - I - I wouldn't say I was brought up to it but - this was the - the drill in school when you met a teacher outside you see, any other teachers in the school or you met the schoolmaster this - this was supposed to be done. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 This was something taught in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh yes, more in the school than in - in the home. Yes.
