\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12058980\charrsid16660515 G}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 aelic language, he was very very fluent in both languages himself, and he - tended to still allow a - the languages in, you - you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 That wasn't common then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 
I would think not - I think that he was a rather exceptional man, and he was an extremely fine public speaker - in both languages. Yes. And - a tremendous with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Was he the one that wrote down some of the stories of the bard you were telling me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 In the school was all the instruction through the medium of English?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Yes. Yes. Oh yes. Our - our first teacher was herself and English - she wasn't a gaelic speaker, she was from outside somewhere. Yes.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Did she have any pupil teachers who could understand what you children said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Yes, there would have been pupil teachers then. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 What would happen to those children like yourself who had come to school really knowing very little English?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 
Yes, well I imagine the pupil teachers would have - would have helped. Yes. I remember - two I think, two pupil teachers being there, and one of them just retired a few years ago, she was a pupil teacher in - during part of my stay - at the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Do you remember whether you were allowed to talk }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12058980\charrsid16660515 G}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
