Do you remember what sort of things the teachers tried to inculcate into the children or did they not try, did they think that things like hygiene and manners were the province of the home rather than the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Possibly at 
that point yes, I - I think - I don't remember - that there was any particular - attention - given to that, maybe there might have been incidents when - something like that was called for. But - generally - I don't - shouldn't think so in the early - in t
he early stages that there was anything like that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Do you remember if punctuality was considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Oh yes, you're late, oh yes, yes, punctuality was very important and regular attendance was very important. And bringing a peat under 
