\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Yes, and their stories would have been related to them in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8199592\charrsid16660515 G}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 aelic you see, yes, the news and that would have been - translated for them.
