\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8863920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Did you get any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3561112 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 Not while I was at home, no. No, there was no place to spend it anyway. When I 
