hem - yes, tend to be a bit - well I don't think so noticeable with the young people - the young people tend to dress more like other people nowadays, you know, there's money around and - and - and they - they get around, some of them go out working, some
 of the girls go to hostels and - and some of the men go out to labouring jobs and that they keep working and - and - and some of them dress extremely well today and you - you would have a - quite a difficulty picking them out.
