upposed - they weren't expected to send their children to school regularly, if they did half the required attend}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4588680\charrsid16660515 anc}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5316270\charrsid16660515 
es they got away with it. As long as they were travelling you see. Yes. But - how much they went to school I think on occasions - we saw the 
